    <title> Représentation des nombres et arithmétique modulaire </title>
    <introduction xml:id= "intro-">  <!-- Ajouter le même identifiant du chapitre après le - du xml:id -->
    
    </introduction>
    <section>
    <title>Problem with intertext</title>
    <p>
    All with left side and intertext
    <mdn>
                <mrow>{\mathcal L}(y')(s)  &amp;= s {\mathcal L}(y)(s) - y(0) = s Y(s) - y(0)</mrow>
                <mrow>{\mathcal L}(y'')(s) &amp;= s^2 {\mathcal L}(y)(s) - sy(0) - y'(0)= s^2 Y(s) - sy(0) - y'(0).</mrow>
                <intertext>And so it follows that,</intertext>
                <mrow>{\mathcal L}(y')(s)^{++}  &amp;= s {\mathcal L}(y)(s) - y(0) = s Y(s) - y(0)</mrow>
                <mrow>{\mathcal L}(y'')(s)^{5} &amp;= s^2 {\mathcal L}(y)(s) - sy(0) - y'(0)= s^2 Y(s) - sy(0) - y'(0).</mrow>
            </mdn>
    No left side and no intertext.
    <mdn>
                <mrow>{\mathcal L}(y')(s)  &amp;= s {\mathcal L}(y)(s) - y(0) = s Y(s) - y(0)</mrow>
                <mrow> &amp;= s^2 {\mathcal L}(y)(s) - sy(0) - y'(0)= s^2 Y(s) - sy(0) - y'(0).</mrow>
                <mrow> &amp;= s {\mathcal L}(y)(s) - y(0) = s Y(s) - y(0)</mrow>
                <mrow>&amp;= s^2 {\mathcal L}(y)(s) - sy(0) - y'(0)= s^2 Y(s) - sy(0) - y'(0).</mrow>
            </mdn>
            no left side and intertext
            <mdn>
                <mrow>{\mathcal L}(y')(s)  &amp;= s {\mathcal L}(y)(s) - y(0) = s Y(s) - y(0)</mrow>
                <mrow>{\mathcal L}(y'')(s) &amp;= s^2 {\mathcal L}(y)(s) - sy(0) - y'(0)= s^2 Y(s) - sy(0) - y'(0).</mrow>
                <intertext>And so it follows that,</intertext>
                <mrow>&amp;= s {\mathcal L}(y)(s) - y(0) = s Y(s) - y(0)</mrow>
                <mrow> &amp;= s^2 {\mathcal L}(y)(s) - sy(0) - y'(0)= s^2 Y(s) - sy(0) - y'(0).</mrow>
            </mdn>
    </p>
